    shall lay
      the pieces,
      the head,
      and the fat
    in order on the wood
    that is on the fire
    which is on the altar;
    # Leviticus 01:09
    but he shall wash its innards and its legs with water.
  }
}

# PresentationSection: \hfill{}$\geqq$01.09b
{
  {
    # Leviticus 01:09b
    The priest shall burn all of it on the altar,
    for a >>burnt offering<<,
    an offering made by fire,
    of a pleasant aroma to Yahweh.
  }
}

