# Section: \hfill{}$\geqq$02.11
{
  {
    # Leviticus 02:11
    No >>meal offering<< which you shall offer to Yahweh
    shall be made with yeast;
    for you shall burn no yeast,
    nor any honey,
    as an offering made by fire to Yahweh.

    # Leviticus 02:12
