    With all your offerings you shall offer salt.
  }
}

# Section: Meal Offering of First Fruits\hfill{}$\geqq$02.14
{
  {
    # Leviticus 02:14
    >>>>If you offer a >>meal offering<< of first fruits to Yahweh,
